gstreamer10: GStreamer (Multimedia framework)
gstreamer10:
gstreamer10: GStreamer is a library that allows the construction of graphs of
gstreamer10: media-handling components, ranging from simple Ogg/Vorbis playback
gstreamer10: to complex audio (mixing) and video (non-linear editing) processing. 
gstreamer10: Applications can take advantage of advances in codec and filter
gstreamer10: technology transparently. Developers can add new codecs and filters
gstreamer10: by writing a simple plugin with a clean, generic interface.
gstreamer10:
gstreamer10: GStreamer is released under the LGPL. 
gstreamer10:
